messages.messageBody:
We are!!  There is me Jana (40'ish-sometimes), Jake 13 and Josh 11--who love to game (Runescape, GTA, a trivia game named Buzz) and ride skateboards, and swim, and make new friends, travel all over America, loves animals & critters of all kind.  Can't wait to meet everyone in the NE now!  Just left LiG in Vancouver a couple wks ago!  Missing the tribe already.
 
See ya'll soon!           Jana-unschooling myself and living life, large & loud with Jake & Josh
